6. VIABILITY TESTING
We tested the MVP with students involved in Fusion Magazine and other fashion-focused students at Pace University.
Feedback included:
Users liked browsing vintage fashion archives
The bookmark feature was useful for saving inspiration
Search filters made finding magazines easier
Changes made:
Improved navigation
Simplified issue browsing
Added clearer bookmark interactions
The testing showed strong interest in digital fashion archives and curated zine subscriptions.

